The%20pair%20settled%20a%20year%20later%2C%20with%20Assi%20getting%20financial%20compensation%20and%20an%20apology%20letter%20that%20could%20be%20shown%20to%20a%20limited%20set%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20the%20documentary%20missed%20out%20on%20Assi's%20journey%20for%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22318f63e5-1862-4210-9b4f-feaa4f224c39%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhogal's%20attorneys%20made%20their%20own%20allegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20of%20a%20South%20Asian%20woman%20wearing%20headphones%20and%20a%20pink%20top%20sitting%20in%20a%20radio%20booth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671125b1a0a0cc14f221b146%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20image%20of%20Kirat%20Assi%20when%20she%20was%20younger%20in%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BSweet%20Bobby%26quot%3B%20documentary.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20episode%20five%20of%20the%202021%20podcast%20series%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tortoisemedia.com%2Flisten%2Fsweet-bobby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESweet%20Bobby%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20publicized%20Assi's%20story%20before%20the%20Netflix%20release%2C%20host%20Alexi%20Mostrous%20said%20that%20Assi%20hired%20two%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmrit%20Maan%20and%20Yair%20Cohen%20helped%20her%20pursue%20legal%20action%20against%20Bhogal%20in%20the%20months%20following%20her%20first%20interactions%20with%20London's%20Metropolitan%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Maan%20tried%20to%20help%20Assi%20get%20the%20police%20to%20investigate%2C%20Cohen%20represented%20Assi%20in%20the%20UK's%20civil%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMostrous%20said%20Assi%20then%20sent%20a%20letter%20threatening%20legal%20action%20against%20Boghal%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20harassment%2C%20misusing%20Assi's%20private%20information%2C%20and%20breaching%20data%20protection%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhogal's%20attorney%20responded%20by%20accusing%20Assi%20of%20grooming%20Bhogal%20because%20the%20online%20relationship%20began%20when%20Bhogal%20was%20a%20child%20and%20Assi%20was%2032%2C%20Mostrous%20reported.%20The%20attorneys%20also%20claimed%20that%20Assi%20always%20knew%20Bhogal%20was%20pretending%20to%20be%20Bobby%20and%20threatened%20to%20go%20public%20with%20the%20allegation%20if%20the%20lawsuit%20wasn't%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssi%20said%20in%20the%20podcast%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20outrageous.%20I%20just%20thought%20that's%20so%20low%20and%20so%20disgusting%20of%20you.%20You've%20already%20confessed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssi%20did%20not%20back%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20episode%20six%20of%20the%20podcast%2C%20Mostrous%20said%20Bhogal%20offered%20a%20payout%20and%20a%20semi-private%20apology%20letter%20to%20settle%20the%20case%20in%20the%20spring%20of%202021.%20Mostrous%20said%20Assi%20wanted%20a%20public%20apology%20but%20accepted%20the%20settlement%20after%20speaking%20to%20her%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22005b259f-792f-4621-8298-48e134af4c39%5C%22%3EAssi%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20police%20to%20investigate%20the%20crime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BSweet%20Bobby%3A%20My%20Catfish%20Nightmare%26quot%3B%20featuring%20an%20image%20of%20a%20south%20Asian%20man%20in%20a%20t-shirt%20in%20a%20frame.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671126d2fd8ede6c99e36c39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20picture%20of%20the%20real%20Bobby%20Jandu%20in%20%26quot%3BSweet%20Bobby%3A%20My%20Catfish%20Nightmare.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Netflix%20documentary%2C%20Assi%20said%20the%20police%20in%20London%20did%20not%20take%20her%20claim%20seriously%20and%20thought%20that%20Jandu%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20the%20real%20victims%20of%20the%20catfishing%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Metropolitan%20Police%20dropped%20the%20case%20in%202019%2C%20citing%20a%20lack%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20was%20again%20investigating%2C%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bactively%20working%20with%26quot%3B%20Assi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20followed%20Assi%20complaining%20about%20the%20handling%20of%20her%20case%20to%20the%20UK's%20Independent%20Office%20for%20Police%20Conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IOPC%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20found%20fault%20with%20the%20initial%20response%20and%20asked%20the%20Met%20to%20review%20its%20investigation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20clear%20precisely%20when%20or%20why%20the%20Met%20reopened%20its%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-sweet-bobby-kirat-assi-get-justice-after-catfished-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729507897000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6711221401ea6d83dee1d841%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-sweet-bobby-kirat-assi-get-justice-after-catfished-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kirat%20Assi%20was%20catfished%20for%20eight%20years.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20her%20legal%20battle%20after%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aadekaiyero%40insider.com%20(Ayomikun%20Adekaiyero)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%20CM%20Omar%20Abdullah%20resigns%20from%20Budgam%2C%20retains%20NCP%20bastion%20Ganderbal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729507407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114425887%2Cimgsize-1201146.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fti