20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Misri%2C%20the%20top%20diplomat%20in%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20(MEA)%2C%20said%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20negotiators%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20had%20held%20several%20rounds%20of%20talks%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20These%20talks%20have%20resulted%20in%20an%20agreement%20on%20%26quot%3Bpatrolling%20arrangements%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20in%20the%20India-China%20border%20areas%20leading%20to%20disengagement%20and%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20had%20risen%20in%20these%20areas%20in%202020%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20announcement%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20hold%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit%20of%20the%20informal%20group%20of%20states%20comprising%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20and%20South%20Africa%20(BRICS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20meeting%20of%20the%20working%20mechanism%20for%20consultation%20and%20coordination%20on%20India-China%20border%20affairs%20was%20held%20on%20August%2029%20in%20Beijing.%20The%20two%20sides%20then%20had%20a%20frank%2C%20constructive%20and%20forward-looking%20exchange%20of%20views%20on%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20to%20narrow%20down%20differences%20and%20find%20early%20resolution%20of%20outstanding%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20agreed%20that%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%2C%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20LAC%20are%20the%20essential%20basis%20for%20restoration%20of%20normalcy%20in%20bilateral%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Indian%20Army%20chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20had%20said%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20resolved%20the%20%26quot%3Blow-hanging%20fruits%26quot%3B%20and%20now%20need%20to%20address%20difficult%20situations%2C%20adding%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20signalling%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20diplomatic%20side%20and%20execution%20on%20the%20ground%20was%20dependent%20on%20military%20commanders%20of%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20and%20Chinese%20military%20commanders%20too%20had%20been%20meeting%20regularly%20seeking%20complete%20disengagement%20in%20the%20remaining%20areas%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20as%20an%20essential%20basis%20for%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20India-China%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20areas%20still%20remained%20to%20be%20de-escalated%20after%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20withdrew%20from%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20in%20Ladakh%20in%20September%202022.%20The%20Chinese%20forces%20in%20this%20area%20had%20returned%20to%20pre-2020%20positions.%20Even%20then%2C%20Chinese%20soldiers%20were%20still%20believed%20to%20hold%20large%20swathes%20of%20Indian%20territory%20to%20the%20north%20in%20the%20Depsang%20plains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFierce%20clashes%20between%20soldiers%20of%20both%20sides%20took%20place%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh's%20Galwan%20in%20June%202020%2C%20in%20which%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20action.%20Over%2040%20Chinese%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20or%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Reuters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729505820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fqcr6vjes_ladakh-generic_625x300_10_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-china-agree-on-patrolling-agreement-along-lac-leads-to-disengagement-6838489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20China%20have%20arrived%20on%20a%20patrolling%20arrangement%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20and%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20disengagement%20and%20resolution%20of%20skirmishes%20that%20began%20in%20May%202020%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20