-a-rapid-descent-into-dystopia-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eretail%20apocalypse%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-financing-urban-planning-pandemic-retail-apocalypse-vacant-storefront-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintensified%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20convenience%20chain%207-Eleven%20just%20announced%20it's%20closing%20hundreds%20of%20stores%20nationwide.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%20feels%20like%20it's%20becoming%20a%20permanent%20feature%20of%20America's%20retail%20landscape.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20nearby%20place%20to%20pop%20into%20and%20grab%20a%20bag%20of%20chips%20or%20a%20bottle%20of%20NyQuil%2C%20you%20may%20be%20out%20of%20luck.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20pharmacies%2C%20the%20reckoning%20has%20been%20triggered%20by%20a%20confluence%20of%20trends%2C%20from%20the%20shift%20to%20online%20shopping%20to%20the%20convoluted%20way%20Americans%20pay%20for%20healthcare.%20For%20a%20while%2C%20the%20pandemic%20actually%20helped%20pharmacies%20paper%20over%20some%20of%20their%20deeper%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20all%20those%20vaccines%20and%20home-test%20kits%20brought%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20business.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20underlying%20issues%20are%20proving%20impossible%20to%20avoid.%20%26quot%3BNone%20of%20these%20things%20is%20a%20new%20factor%2C%26quot%3B%20Elizabeth%20Anderson%2C%20a%20senior%20managing%20director%20and%20healthcare-equity%20research%20analyst%20at%20Evercore%20ISI%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20compound%20that%20for%20years%20and%20years%20and%20years%2C%20and%20eventually%20you%20get%20to%20kind%20of%20a%20breaking%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBig%20chains%20like%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWalgreens%20and%20CVS%20make%20their%20money%20in%20two%20main%20ways%3A%20selling%20prescriptions%20in%20the%20back%20of%20their%20stores%20and%20selling%20everyday%20goods%20out%20front.%20The%20problem%20for%20companies%20is%20that%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20business%20are%20under%20pressure%20from%20outside%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20there's%20the%20rise%20of%20e-commerce.%20In%20the%20age%20of%20Amazon%2C%20people%20can%20buy%20toilet%20paper%20and%20ibuprofen%20and%20greeting%20cards%20and%20snacks%20online%20and%20have%20them%20delivered%20right%20to%20their%20door%2C%20often%20at%20lower%20prices.%20Not%20to%20mention%20no%20hunting%20around%20for%20an%20associate%20to%20open%20a%20glass%20case.%20(Amazon%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F08%2F02%2Famazon-drug-store-thefts-online-customer-boost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20actually%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20lousy%20experience%20at%20brick-and-mortar%20pharmacies%20has%20been%20a%20boost%20to%20its%20business.)%20On%20the%20retail%20level%2C%20pharmacies%20are%20also%20competing%20with%20big-box%20stores%20like%20Walmart%20or%20Target%2C%20as%20well%20as%20cheaper%20options%20like%20Dollar%20General%2C%20which%20has%20been%20working%20to%20win%20over%20budget-conscious%20consumers.%20The%20more%20expensive%20and%20less%20convenient%20pharmacies%20become%2C%20the%20more%20customers%20defect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChain%20pharmacies%20are%20competing%20with%20not%20just%20their%20rivals%20for%20retail%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20themselves.%20As%20Walgreens%20and%20CVS%20stores%20have%20proliferated%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so%2C%20many%20of%20their%20locations%20are%20basically%20right%20on%20top%20of%20each%20other.%20It's%20tough%20to%20make%20a%20store%20profitable%20when%20there's%20an%20identical%20one%20two%20blocks%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWalgreens%20and%20CVS%20have%20been%20on%20a%20massive%20expansionary%20push%2C%26quot%3B%20Neil%20Saunders%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20retail%20consultancy%20GlobalData%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20just%20opened%20stores%20willy-nilly%2C%20and%20they've%20ended%20up%20with%20portfolios%20that%20are%20too%20big.%20There's%20too%20much%20overlap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20business%2C%20pharmacies%20are%20expensive%20to%20run.%20Renting%20the%20physical%20space%20and%20paying%20an%20educated%20workforce%20of%20pharmacists%20mean%20that%20the%20fixed%20costs%20are%20high.%20There's%20not%20a%20ton%20of%20room%20for%20cutting%20corners%2C%20except%20for%20downsizing%20the%20workforce%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20customer%20experience%20worse.%20The%20pharmacy%20end%20of%20the%20business%20is%20also%20under%20pressure%20from%20mail-order%20operations%20and%20from%20grocery%20stores%20and%20big-box%20chains%20like%20Walmart%2C%20which%20have%20added%20pharmacies%20in%20some%20of%20their%20locations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20costs%20and%20competition%2C%20revenues%20at%20the%20big%20chains%20are%20being%20further%20squeezed%20by%20pharmacy%20benefit%20managers%2C%20who%20serve%20as%20the%20industry's%20middlemen.%20Pharmacies%20order%20drugs%20directly%20from%20manufacturers%2C%20dispense%20them%20to%20a%20patient%2C%20and%20are%20then%20reimbursed%20by%20the%20PBMs%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20patient's%20insurer.%20But%20PBMs%20have%20been%20lowering%20the%20rates%20at%20which%20pharmacies%20are%20paid%20for%20handing%20out%20prescriptions%20%E2%80%94%20generally%20their%20top%20source%20of%20revenue.%20Sometimes%20the%20reimbursements%20are%20actually%20lower%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20acquiring%20the%20drug%20%E2%80%94%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncpa.org%2Fnewsroom%2Fqam%2F2023%2F11%2F01%2Flocal-pharmacies-say-theyre-struggling-afford-glp-1s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epharmacies%20say%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20happening%20with%20GLP-1s%20like%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20simple%20part%20is%20that%20prescriptions%20are%20not%20profitable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Douglas%20Hoey%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20National%20Community%20Pharmacists%20Association%2C%20which%20represents%20independent%20pharmacies.%20PBMs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bjudge%2C%20jury%2C%20and%20executioner%26quot%3B%20on%20who%20gets%20paid%20what%2C%20and%20pharmacies%20from%20Walgreens%20to%20the%20little%20shop%20down%20the%20street%20don't%20have%20much%20power%20to%20push%20back.%20%26quot%3BThe%20pharmacy%20really%20doesn't%20have%20any%20negotiating%20leverage%20because%20the%20PBM%20says%2C%20'Well%2C%20pharmacy%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20give%20me%20everything%20I%20ask%20for%2C%20then%20I'm%20going%20to%20not%20allow%20patients%20to%20get%20their%20drug%20benefit%20at%20your%20pharmacy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20larger%20chains%20should%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20be%20able%20to%20weather%20the%20storm%20better%20than%20smaller%20shops.%20After%20all%2C%20they've%20got%20the%20scale%20and%20leverage%20a%20mom-and-pop%20operation%20lacks.%20But%20even%20with%20their%20market%20dominance%2C%20they're%20no%20match%20for%20the%20PBMs.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20Walgreens%20tried%20to%20push%20back%20against%20Express%20Scripts%2C%20a%20major%20PBM%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20earn%20more%20from%20prescriptions.%20Walgreens%20ultimately%20gave%20in%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2012%2F07%2F20%2Fbusiness%2Fwalgreen-and-express-scripts-settle-their-dispute.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elosing%20an%20estimated%20%244%20billion%20in%20the%20battle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20(CVS%20has%20a%20leg%20up%20in%20this%20area%20because%20it%20owns%20Caremark%2C%20one%20of%20the%20big%20three%20PBMs.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20pharmacies%20falter%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20store%2C%20they%20create%20a%20negative%20feedback%20loop%20in%20the%20front.%20Walgreens%20was%20never%20the%20best%20place%20to%20get%20many%20staples%2C%20given%20the%20high%20prices%20and%20limited%20selection%2C%20but%20customers%20could%20be%20counted%20on%20to%20grab%20a%20few%20items%20as%20they%20walked%20down%20the%20aisles%20to%20pick%20up%20their%20prescriptions.%20Now%20that%20more%20and%20more%20patients%20are%20getting%20their%20medications%20by%20mail%20or%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20the%20retail%20end%20has%20dried%20up.%20Pharmacies%20%26quot%3Bwere%20never%20designed%20to%20be%20an%20appealing%20place%20to%20go%20and%20get%20toilet%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jason%20Goldberg%2C%20the%20chief%20commerce-strategy%20officer%20at%20Publicis%20Groupe%2C%20a%20global%20marketing%20firm.%20%26quot%3BToilet%20paper%20was%20a%20profitable%20item%20to%20sell%20to%20someone%20that%20came%20in%20for%20a%20Lipitor%20prescription%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWalgreens%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20But%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20CVS%20told%20me%20that%20the%20company%20was%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20place%20now%26quot%3B%20than%20it%20was%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20The%20decision%20to%20shutter%20stores%20was%20made%20back%20in%202021%2C%20they%20said%2C%20based%20on%20factors%20like%20%26quot%3Bpopulation%20shifts%2C%20consumer%20buying%20patterns%2C%20and%20a%20community's%20store%20density.%26quot%3B%20Even%20after%20the%20%26quot%3Brealignment%26quot%3B%20is%20finished%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added%2C%2085%25%20of%20Americans%20will%20still%20live%20within%2010%20miles%20of%20a%20CVS%20pharmacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20more%20and%20more%20pharmacies%20close%20their%20doors%2C%20Americans%20ultimately%20have%20fewer%20places%20to%20shop%20in%20person.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20decline%20of%20pharmacies%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20how%20badly%20they've%20handled%20the%20retail%20end%20of%20their%20operations.%20For%20starters%2C%20faceless%20chains%20supplanting%20independent%20pharmacies%20diminished%20the%20loyalty%20customers%20felt%20for%20their%20local%20stores.%20In%20a%20mom-and-pop%20location%2C%20you%20could%20develop%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20pharmacist%2C%20get%20trusted%20counseling%2C%20and%20have%20a%20pleasant%20conversation%20about%20how%20your%20kid's%20soccer%20team%20is%20faring.%20In%20the%20current%20landscape%20of%20commoditized%20pharmacies%2C%20there's%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20personalized%20service.%20Waits%20to%20pick%20up%20prescriptions%20are%20long%2C%20customer%20service%20is%20often%20subpar%2C%20and%20if%20you%20do%20have%20a%20problem%2C%20places%20are%20often%20so%20understaffed%20they%20can't%20help%20even%20if%20they%20want%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pharmacy%20experience%2C%20to%20put%20it%20plainly%2C%20often%20sucks.%20In%20many%20places%2C%20there's%20no%20longer%20such%20a%20thing%20as%20a%20quick%2C%20easy%20run%20to%20a%20Duane%20Reade.%20Whether%20you%20believe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-we-dont-actually-know-whether-retail-theft-big-problem-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eretail%20theft%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20as%20big%20a%20problem%20as%20some%20executives%20say%20it%20is%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20items%20are%20now%20locked%20away%2C%20which%20eats%20into%20sales%20and%20leads%20customers%20to%20shop%20elsewhere.%20Brian%20Tanquilut%2C%20a%20healthcare-services-equity%20research%20analyst%20at%20Jefferies%2C%20said%20pharmacies%20were%20also%20narrowing%20their%20stock-keeping-unit%20counts%20%E2%80%94%20basically%2C%20the%20number%20of%20items%20they%20keep%20in%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20to%20better%20manage%20cash%20flows%20and%20inventories%2C%20but%20the%20move%20means%20there%20are%20fewer%20options%20for%20customers.%20I've%20often%20found%20myself%20frustrated%20by%20all%20the%20empty%20shelves%20at%20my%20local%20pharmacy%2C%20and%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20feel%20the%20same%20way.%20From%20a%20consumer%20standpoint%2C%20it%20starts%20to%20feel%20like%2C%20what's%20even%20the%20point%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPharmacies%20don't%20need%20to%20lose%2050%25%20of%20their%20retail%20traffic%20for%20it%20to%20be%20a%20disaster%2C%20Goldberg%20told%20me.%20Just%2010%25%20is%20enough.%20And%20things%20can%20go%20into%20a%20tailspin%2C%20fast.%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%2010%25%20less%20traffic%2C%20so%20you%20sell%20a%20little%20less%20stuff%2C%20so%20you%20staff%20one%20less%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20make%20a%20few%20more%20customers%20dissatisfied.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20convenience%20chains%20are%20also%20struggling%20to%20hang%20on%20to%20their%20customers.%20People%20aren't%20popping%20into%207-Elevens%20as%20often%20as%20they%20used%20to%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20because%20they%20aren't%20commuting%20to%20and%20from%20work%20as%20often%2C%20and%20in%20part%20because%20they%20aren't%20smoking%20as%20much%20and%20don't%20need%20to%20grab%20a%20pack%20of%20cigarettes.%20(Healthier%20habits%2C%20apparently%2C%20are%20bad%20for%20business.)%20What's%20more%2C%20price-conscious%20consumers%20are%20now%20going%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20seek%20out%20lower%20prices%2C%20stopping%20by%20the%20local%20dollar%20store%20for%20some%20cut-rate%20options.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThings%20are%20very%20cyclical%20in%20retail%2C%20and%20you%20see%20the%20rise%20and%20fall%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20formats%20and%20chains%2C%26quot%3B%20Saunders%2C%20the%20retail%20consultant%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20period%20when%20the%20drugstores%20were%20on%20the%20ascendancy%2C%20and%20the%20independent%20chains%20were%20really%20on%20a%20downward%20curve.%20Now%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20is%20drugstores%20having%20gone%20past%20their%20peak%2C%20and%20now%20they're%20in%20a%20very%20difficult%20spot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Walgreens%20closing%20stores%2C%20Saunders%20was%20blunt%20about%20the%20company's%20future.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20got%20to%20set%20out%20a%20pathway%20to%20growth%2C%20both%20to%20convince%20investors%20and%20to%20stabilize%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20that%20they%20have%20done%20that%20convincingly%20yet.%20They%20are%20very%20focused%20on%20managing%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20business%2C%20trying%20to%20change%20the%20business%20structurally%20and%20in%20organizational%20terms%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20really%20set%20out%20a%20proposition%2C%20especially%20for%20how%20they%20win%20in%20retail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20strange%20to%20mourn%20the%20demise%20of%20corporate%20giants%20like%20Walgreens%20and%207-Eleven.%20These%2C%20after%20all%2C%20are%20the%20very%20corporations%20that%20helped%20decimate%20local%20businesses%2C%20from%20the%20friendly%20neighborhood%20pharmacy%20to%20the%20five-and-dime.%20But%20their%20passing%20feels%20like%20it%20marks%20yet%20another%20transitional%20moment%20in%20American%20culture%2C%20as%20the%20entire%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Brunning%20out%20to%20the%20store%20for%20a%20minute%26quot%3B%20goes%20the%20way%20of%20music%20on%20MTV%20and%20the%20landline.%20What%20does%20it%20mean%20to%20have%20so%20few%20places%20left%20to%20grab%20the%20things%20we%20need%3F%20What%20will%20we%20become%20of%20us%20when%20every%20last%20transaction%2C%20from%20our%20Slurpees%20to%20our%20statins%2C%20is%20handled%20electronically%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20minimum%2C%20the%20struggles%20of%20pharmacies%20like%20Walgreens%20mean%20that%20more%20Americans%20will%20now%20have%20no%20place%20to%20fill%20their%20prescriptions%20within%20striking%20distance%20of%20their%20homes.%20An%20estimated%2015.8%20million%20people%20%E2%80%94%20about%204.7%25%20of%20the%20population%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fhealthaffairsscholar%2Farticle%2F2%2F4%2Fqxae035%2F7630415%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealready%20live%20in%20pharmacy%20deserts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Some%20pharmacies%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F10%2F22%2Fdrugstore-close-pharmacy-deserts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshuttering%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20communities%20of%20color%20and%20moving%20to%20whiter%20areas.%20And%20rural%20communities%2C%20which%20often%20have%20only%20a%20single%20pharmacy%20in%20town%2C%20could%20be%20hit%20especially%20hard%20by%20the%20widespread%20closings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20talking%20about%20closing%20a%20store%20that%20not%20only%20is%20important%20for%20a%20community%20for%20their%20prescriptions%2C%20but%20they%20can%20pick%20up%20other%20supplies%20at%20that%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20Nick%20Fabrizio%2C%20a%20senior%20health-policy%20lecturer%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20gone%2C%20now%20they're%20driving%2020%20miles%20or%2030%20miles%20to%20find%20another%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%2C%20there%20are%20no%20obvious%20fixes.%20Steven%20Anderson%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Chain%20Drug%20Stores%2C%20said%20there's%20an%20%26quot%3Burgent%20need%26quot%3B%20for%20congressional%20action%20on%20PBMs%2C%20which%20are%20already%20under%20scrutiny%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F09%2Fftc-sues-prescription-drug-middlemen-artificially-inflating-insulin-drug-prices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernment%20regulators%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20competitors%20like%20Amazon%20aren't%20going%20anywhere%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FWalgreens.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWalgreens.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20isn't%20exactly%20an%20online%20behemoth.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20a%20multifactorial%20problem%20that%20I%20don't%20see%20getting%20better%20anytime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Fabrizio%20said.%20And%20as%20pharmacies%20and%20other%20quick-stop%20stores%20continue%20to%20close%20their%20doors%2C%20we%20may%20look%20back%20one%20day%20in%20the%20not-too-distant%20future%20and%20realize%20we%20were%20living%20through%20the%20golden%20age%20of%20convenience%2C%20when%20getting%20whatever%20you%20needed%20was%20always%20right%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmacy-cvs-walgreens-problems-desert-7-eleven-convenience-store-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729502822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712c00301ea6d83dee28b05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmacy-cvs-walgreens-problems-desert-7-eleven-convenience-store-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chain%20pharmacies%20are%20flashing%20warning%20signs%20and%20shuttering%20stores.%207-Eleven%2