0Unlawful%20Acts%20against%20the%20Safety%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(SUASCA)%20Act%2C%201982%2C%20and%20consultations%20for%20this%20are%20being%20held%20with%20other%20ministries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20last%20week%2C%20eight%20flights%20have%20been%20diverted.%20Each%20threat%20is%20assessed%20individually%20and%20our%20response%20has%20been%20efficient%20and%20dynamic.%20We%20are%20also%20not%20compromising%20on%20safety%20and%20security.%20Even%20though%20most%20of%20them%20are%20hoax%20threats%2C%20we%20cannot%20take%20them%20lightly.%20The%20lives%20of%20passengers%20are%20important%2C%20the%20security%20situation%20is%20important%20and%20protocol%20is%20important.%20We%20have%20enhanced%20security%20at%20airports%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20the%20protocol%20is%20very%20rigid%20and%20strict%20procedures%20have%20to%20be%20followed%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20said%20several%20meetings%20have%20been%20held%20with%20airlines%20and%20their%20opinion%20has%20been%20sought%20to%20minimise%20inconvenience%20to%20them%20as%20well%20as%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20working%20towards%20a%20common%20goal.%20Even%20one%20plane%20getting%20diverted%20or%20delayed%20is%20not%20what%20we%20want...%20There%20has%20to%20be%20some%20kind%20of%20deterrent%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20with%20our%20planned%20amendments%20to%20the%20rules%20and%20the%20Act.%20We%20are%20working%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20and%20state%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20investigations%20into%20the%20threats.%20The%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20passengers%20and%20their%20convenient%20travel%20is%20our%20utmost%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20collective%20efforts%20of%20everyone%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20see%20a%20much%20better%20picture%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20