nes-changes-turnaround-plan-assigned-seats-routes-bags-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Airlines%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElliott%2C%20which%20built%20an%2011%25%20stake%20in%20the%20US%20airline%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20new%20CEO%20and%20board%20members.%20The%20firm%20also%20told%20Southwest%20to%20review%20its%20operations%20and%20develop%20a%20plan%20to%20improve%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest's%20stock%20has%20shed%20nearly%20half%20its%20value%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20and%20its%20passenger%20volumes%20are%20below%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20despite%20strong%20travel%20demand.%20On%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20July%2C%20company%20executives%20said%20revenues%20were%20hurt%20because%20Southwest%20did%20not%20optimize%20summer%20demand%20and%20faced%20overstaffing%20because%20of%20Boeing's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-delays-wreak-havoc-with-airline-industrys-plans-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplane%20delivery%20delays%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest's%20CEO%2C%20Bob%20Jordan%2C%20has%20been%20with%20the%20company%20for%20three%20decades%20and%20was%20appointed%20as%20chief%20in%202022.%20Elliott%20said%20Jordan%20and%20chairman%20Gary%20Kelly%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20company's%20underperformance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20activist%20hedge%20fund%20started%20its%20public%20campaign%20against%20Southwest's%20leadership%20in%20June%20and%20called%20for%20a%20December%2010%20shareholder%20vote%20to%20decide%20on%20Elliott's%20eight%20board%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest's%2015-member%20board%20consists%20of%2013%20independent%20members%2C%20according%20to%20a%20filing.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20intends%20to%20appoint%20four%20new%20independent%20directors%2C%20potentially%20including%20some%20of%20those%20proposed%20by%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElliott%20said%20its%20%26quot%3BStronger%20Southwest%26quot%3B%20podcast%20will%20have%20one-on-one%20conversations%20with%20the%20firm's%20nominated%20directors.%20The%20first%20episode%20%E2%80%94%20an%20interview%20with%20former%20WestJet%20CEO%C2%A0Gregg%20Saretsky%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0was%20released%20last%20week%20on%20platforms%20including%20Apple%20Podcasts%20and%20Spotify.%20The%20video%20version%20has%203%2C900%20views%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%20before%20the%20first%20episode%20dropped%2C%20the%20airline%20started%20making%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20are%20likely%20on%20the%20way.%20Last%20month%2C%20Southwest%20introduced%20a%20dramatic%20turnaround%20plan%2C%20scrapping%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-airlines-history-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eunique%20playbook%20of%20more%20than%2050%20years%2C%20which%20included%20open%20seating%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favor%20of%20becoming%20an%20airline%20that%20resembles%20most%20of%20its%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20and%20Elliott%20are%20now%20working%20on%20a%20settlement%20that%20would%20give%20the%20hedge%20fund%20representation%20without%20controlling%20Southwest's%20board%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-10-20%2Fsouthwest-looks-for-truce-with-elliott-after-major-policy-tweaks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20unclear%20if%20new%20episodes%20of%20the%20podcast%20will%20still%20be%20released%20amid%20settlement%20talks%2C%20communication%20strategists%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Elliott's%20novel%20move%20has%20benefits%2C%20including%20cost-effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8daa6d8-8149-4352-a143-8815af696f72%5C%22%3ECheaper%20and%20more%20direct%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20activist%20investors%20have%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecommunicated%20directly%20with%20investors%2C%20because%20most%20companies%20have%2010%20to%2020%20major%20shareholders%20who%20decide%20their%20elections%2C%20said%20Scott%20Bisang%2C%20a%20founding%20partner%20of%20financial%20communications%20firm%20Collected%20Strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20companies%20like%20Southwest%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-heirs-shareholder-letter-nelson-peltz-hostile-takover-bob-iger-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%2C%20which%20saw%20similar%20activist%20interest%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20individual%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20call%20every%20retail%20shareholder%2C%20and%20sending%20direct%20mail%20to%20every%20holder%20multiple%20times%20is%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Bisang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20podcast%20allows%20the%20activist%20to%20completely%20control%20the%20content%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20media%20outlet%20shaping%20an%20interview.%20Shareholders%20may%20subscribe%20to%20the%20podcast%20and%20get%20notifications%20directly%2C%20which%20could%20create%20a%20recurring%20benefit%20if%20they%20watch%20more%20than%20one%20episode.%20If%20lots%20of%20people%20subscribe%2C%20the%20activist%20could%20collect%20data%20and%20retarget%20ads%20to%20investors%20through%20other%20channels%2C%20Bisang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20podcast%2C%20Elliott%20rolled%20out%20a%20website%20and%20accounts%20on%20Instagram%2C%20X%2C%20and%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECas%20Sydorowitz%2C%20the%20global%20CEO%20of%20shareholder%20engagement%20service%20Georgeson%2C%20said%20an%20activist's%20podcast%20could%20go%20beyond%20investors%2C%20since%20employees%2C%20customers%2C%20and%20suppliers%20might%20also%20listen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20understand%20the%20need%20to%20communicate%20with%20shareholders%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20to%20garner%20support%20for%20their%20director%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20Sydorowitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BHosting%20a%20podcast%20is%20a%20new%20and%20potentially%20effective%20way%20for%20an%20activist%20to%20showcase%20the%20qualifications%20of%20their%20director%20candidates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8a88bd5-62cd-48d8-9b2d-a2d413d0c090%5C%22%3EPodcasts%20are%20the%20new%20activist%20battleground%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Disney%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20proxy%20war%20against%20activist%20investor%20Nelson%20Peltz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Disney's%20annual%20meeting%20in%20April%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshareholders%20voted%20to%20keep%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20and%20Disney%20management's%20board%20and%20rejected%20the%20activist's%20two%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20Disney%20didn't%20do%20its%20own%20podcast%20series%20last%20year%2C%20they%20actually%20advertised%20heavily%20on%20entertainment%20podcasts%20like%20'The%20Town%2C'%26quot%3B%20a%20podcast%20about%20Hollywood%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Bisang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Southwest%20battle%20continues%2C%20he%20said%20to%20expect%20direct%20paid%20ad%20campaigns%20from%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20different%20than%20what%20we%20see%20with%20a%20presidential%20election%2C%20except%20in%20a%20proxy%20fight%2C%20you%20can%20target%20advertising%20much%20more%20specifically%20on%20your%20investor%20base%20versus%20every%20voter%20in%20a%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Bisang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20and%20Elliott%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felliott-podcast-southwest-airlines-activism-communication-reach-retail-investors-directors-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729500469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6711fdefa0a0cc14f221ea6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felliott-podcast-southwest-airlines