%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-world-summit-2024-india-century-live-updates-pm-narendra-modi-david-cameron-s-jaishankar-to-speak-6830644%5C%22%3ENDTV%20World%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20Lord%20David%20Cameron%20said%20the%20world%20needs%20strong%20economic%20growth%2C%20more%20democracy%20and%20a%20green%20transition%20to%20deal%20with%20climate%20change%20and%20India%20is%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20all%20three%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cameron's%20session%20at%20the%20Summit%20was%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-on-path-of-unprecedented-growth-pms-top-quotes-at-ndtv-world-summit-6836611%5C%22%3Ekeynote%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20former%20UK%20prime%20minister%20began%20by%20commenting%20on%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20great%20to%20hear%20PM%20Modi's%20speech.%20To%20have%20that%20energy%20level%20at%20the%20start%20of%20your%20third%20term%20is%20truly%20impressive...%20I%20made%20it%20into%20a%20second%20term%20(as%20UK%20prime%20minister)%20but%20since%20then%20we%20have%20had%20quite%20a%20number%20of%20prime%20ministers.%20We%20have%20not%20had%20anyone%20having%20three%20terms%20since%20Tony%20Blair%20and%20Margaret%20Thatcher%20before%20him.%20It%20(PM%20Modi's%20third%20term)%20is%20very%20impressive%20because%20it%20means%20you%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20get%20real%20change%2C%20real%20things%20done%20in%20a%20very%20consistent%20way%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20India%20Century%2C%20Mr%20Cameron%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20reset%20because%20the%20world%20has%20changed%20%26quot%3Bhugely%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20institutions%20were%20set%20up%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20the%20rise%20of%20India%2C%20which%20will%20probably%20become%20the%20world's%20largest%20economy%20at%20some%20stage%20in%20this%20century.%20So%2C%20obviously%2C%20we%20need%20a%20reset%20and%20countries%20like%20India%20should%20be%20at%20its%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20his%20statement%20from%202015%20that%20India%20should%20have%20a%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20Mr%20Cameron%20said%20that%20should%20be%20India's%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20need%20reform%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20and%20I%20made%20this%20argument%20as%20far%20back%20as%202005.%20When%20I%20became%20leader%20of%20the%20Conservative%20Party%2C%20India%20was%20the%20first%20country%20I%20visited%20outside%20Europe.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20country%20I%20visited%20outside%20Europe%20when%20I%20became%20prime%20minister%20in%202010.%20I%20like%20to%20think%20that%20I%20was%20an%20early%20believer%20in%20the%20Indian%20Century.%20Obviously%2C%20a%20permanent%20seat%20on%20the%20Security%20Council%20should%20be%20India's%20right%20in%20this%20changed%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20changing%20these%20institutions%20would%20take%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20former%20UK%20prime%20minister%20said%20it%20was%20good%20to%20see%20India%20take%20its%20place%20in%20institutions%20like%20the%20Quad%20and%20the%20G20.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20G7%20regularly%20invites%20India%20to%20attend%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20standing%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFree%20Trade%20Agreement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20free%20trade%20agreement%20(FTA)%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Boris%20Johnson%20had%20said%20would%20be%20concluded%20by%20Diwali%20in%202022%2C%20Mr%20Cameron%20said%20it%20was%20a%20pity%20it%20hadn't%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20has%20not%20happened%20for%20a%20good%20reason.%20Britain%20and%20India%20both%20understand%20that%20you%20get%20only%20one%20chance%20to%20make%20an%20FTA%20and%20you%20have%20to%20make%20it%20a%20good%20one%2C%20which%20means%20both%20sides%20have%20to%20put%20more%20on%20the%20table.%20My%20plea%2C%20which%20I%20will%20be%20making%20to%20the%20foreign%20minister%20when%20I%20see%20him%20this%20afternoon%2C%20is%20that%20let's%20make%20our%20deal%20as%20good%20and%20as%20big%20and%20as%20generous%20(as%20possible)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Cameron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20we%20have%20to%20cover%20scotch%20whisky%20and%20IT%20workers%20for%20India.%20We%20need%20Indian%20investment%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20trade%20with%20India%2C%20but%20also%20India%20needs%20the%20millions%20of%20jobs%20being%20created%20every%20year.%20So%20it%20is%20win-win%2C%20but%20we%20should%20both%20put%20more%20on%20the%20table%20and%20take%20some%20more%20risk%2C%20including%20political%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cameron%20stressed%20that%20doing%20so%20was%20also%20important%20for%20India%20because%20it%20would%20set%20the%20standard%20for%20its%20deal%20with%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShift%20In%20Perception%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20when%20he%20thought%20the%20West's%20perception%20of%20India%20shifted%2C%20the%20former%20UK%20prime%20minister%20said%20there%20have%20been%20various%20moments%2C%20including%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20first%20successful%20landing%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole.%20For%20him%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it%20was%20the%20year%20that%20Indian%20investment%20in%20the%20UK%20overtook%20Japanese%20investment%20because%20of%20the%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover%20deal%20by%20the%20Tata%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20so%20many%20moments%20in%20India's%20recent%20history%20which%20have%20woken%20people%20up%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20this%20great%20country%20-%20the%20opening%20in%201991%2C%20the%20moment%20when%20it%20was%20clear%20India's%20population%20would%20overtake%20China%2C%20this%20huge%20green%20transition%20and%20green%20investment%2C%20and%20the%20lunar%20mission%2C%20which%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20moment%20when%20the%20whole%20world%20saw%20what%20the%20potential%20of%20India%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Cameron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20answer%2C%20though%2C%20would%20be%20a%20bit%20more%20parochial.%20It%20was%20the%20year%20when%20Indian%20investment%20in%20the%20UK%20overtook%20Japanese%20investment%20because%20of%20the%20massive%20investment%20in%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover.%20Here%20was%20this%20great%20iconic%20business%2C%20Tata%20-%20obviously%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20who%20was%20an%20advisor%20to%20me%20as%20prime%20minister%20-%20an%20Indian%20company%20coming%20into%20Britain%2C%20taking%20over%20one%20of%20our%20most%20famous%20car%20brands%2C%20investing%20in%20it%2C%20growing%20it%20and%20improving%20it.%20That%2C%20to%20me%2C%20was%20a%20real%20wake-up%20call%20that%20this%20economy%20has%20arrived%20on%20the%20global%20stage%20and%20is%20going%20to%20do%20great%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Students%20In%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20anti-immigration%20rhetoric%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20its%20possible%20impact%20on%20Indian%20students%2C%20who%20make%20up%20the%20biggest%20cohort%20of%20international%20students%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Mr%20Cameron%20made%20a%20distinction%20between%20that%20and%20illegal%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20prime%20minister%20said%20there%20is%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20students%20that%20can%20study%20at%20British%20universities%20and%20the%20UK%20wants%20as%20many%20to%20come%20as%20possible%20because%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20industry%26quot%3B%20for%20them%20and%20builds%20great%20connections%20between%20the%20UK%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pushed%20for%20taking%20student%20numbers%20out%20of%20immigration%20numbers%20and%20said%20the%20real%20problem%20in%20the%20UK%20was%20illegal%20migration%20from%20countries%20like%20Syria%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Iran%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia-Ukraine%20Mediation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cameron%20said%20the%20world%20is%20seeing%20conflicts%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20situation%20and%20stressed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20reestablish%20norms%20of%20behaviour.%20Referring%20to%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20he%20said%20he%20could%20not%20think%20of%20a%20clearer%20example%20in%20his%20political%20lifetime%20of%20one%20country%20invading%20another%20with%20no%20excuse%20or%20justification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20India%20could%20play%20the%20role%20of%20mediator%20given%20PM%20Modi's%20earlier%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20his%20upcoming%20visit%20to%20Russia%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit%2C%20Mr%20Cameron%20said%20India%20has%20the%20credibility%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20get%20back%20to%20some%20clear%20norms.%20This%20country%20(India)%20has%20suffered%20terribly%20from%20terrorism%2C%20so%20has%20my%20own.%20We%20need%20to%20have%20an%20understanding%20that%20there%20are%20no%20good%20terrorists%20and%20bad%20terrorists.%20We%20need%20to%20get%20back%20to%20the%20understanding%20that%20a%20country's%20borders%20are%2C%20or%20should%20be%2C%20inviolable...%20I%20know%20in%20the%20West%20we%20are%20accused%20of%20double%20standards%20and%20we%20have%20made%20mistakes%2C%20obviously%20referring%20to%20Iraq%2C%20but%20two%20wrongs%20don't%20make%20a%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what's%20happening%20at%20India's%20border%20with%20China%2C%20Mr%20Cameron%20said%20that%20ties%20in%20with%20his%20point%20on%20territorial%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20the%20most%20grotesque%20violation%20of%20a%20country's%20borders%2C%20as%20you%20have%20with%20Ukraine%2C%20we%20all%20need%20to%20stand%20together%20and%20say%20to%20Russia%20that%20what%20has%20happened%20is%20wrong.%20India%20might%20well%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20try%20and%20provide%20some%20mediation%2C%20but%20it%20must%20be%20mediation%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20Vladimir%20Putin%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20territory%20by%20force%20and%20be%20rewarded.%20We%20know%20from%20our%20history%20that%20if%20you%20reward%20people%20for%20taking%20territory%20by%20force%2C%20they%20come%20back%20and%20take%20some%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Brooke%20Bond%2C%20James%20Bond'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cameron%20recalled%20PM%20Modi's%20reception%20at%20London's%20Wembley%20stadium%20in%202015%20and%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bquite%20an%20occasion%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20you%20don't%20forget%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20UK%20-%20if%20you're%20lucky%20-%20as%20a%20prime%20minister%20or%20the%20party%20leader%2C%20you%20might%20speak%20to%203%2C000-4%2C000%20people%20at%20your%20party%20conference.%20But%20to%20go%20to%20Wembley%20Stadium%20and%20introduce%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20where%20you%20are%20speaking%20to%2085%2C000%20people%2C%20that%20was%20quite%20an%20occasion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20at%20that%20event%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20about%20his%20Conservative%20Party%20giving%20the%20UK%20the%20first%20woman%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20first%20Jewish%20prime%20minister%20and%20that%20he%20was%20sure%20the%20country%20would%20have%20the%20first%20British%20Indian%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20said%20that%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20there%20was%20a%20young%20man%20in%20the%20back%20row%2C%20called%20Rishi%20Sunak.%20He%20was%20at%20that%20speech%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi...%20PM%20Modi%20made%20a%20very%20powerful%20speech%2C%20I%20remember%20he%20was%20talking%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20UK%20and%20India%20and%20he%20had%20this%20great%20riff%20on%20tea%2C%20movies%20and%20finance.%20It%20was%20Brooke%20Bond%2C%20James%20Bond%20and%20Rupee%20Bond.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20very%20snappy%20soundbite%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Rishi%20Sunak%20Very%20Capable'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cameron%20also%20said%20it%20was%20an%20honour%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20under%20Rishi%20Sunak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20admired%20him.%20I%20think%20we%20was%20a%20very%20good%20prime%20minister.%20He%20is%20extremely%20hard-working%2C%20highly%20intelligent%2C%20very%20capable%2C%20very%20good%20at%20bringing%20people%20together...%20He%20had%20a%20very%20difficult%20inheritance%2C%20I%20think%20the%20year%20of%20three%20prime%20ministers%20was%20probably%20impossible%20to%20recover%20from%2C%20but%20Rishi%20brought%20stability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20can%20be%20proud%20that%20someone%20whose%20parents%20had%20arrived%20in%20Britain%20from%20India...%20that%20within%20two%20generations%20he%20has%20the%20most%20important%20job%20in%20the%20country.%20I%20think%20that%20reflects%20well%20on%20Britain...%20It%20is%20remarkable%2C%20it%20is%20a%20great%20testament%20to%20our%20country%20and%20to%20your%20talent%20that%20this%20is%20possible%2C%20and%20this%20has%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20said.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729496460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ffkrrv3uo_david-cameron-_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-needs-permanent-seat-at-un-security-council-david-