%22published%22%3A1729495361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsuraj-estate-developers-raises-rs-343-cr-via-issue-of-shares-to-expand-biz-124102100314_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20incorporation%2C%20Suraj%20Estate%20Developers%20has%20completed%2042%20projects%20with%20a%20developed%20area%20of%20more%20than%201%2C046%2C543.20%20square%20feet%20in%20the%20South-Central%20Mumbai%20region%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsuraj-estate-developers-raises-rs-343-cr-via-issue-of-shares-to-expand-biz-124102100314_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CEO%20Denies%20Employee's%202-Day%20Leave%20Request%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20Have%202%20Critical%20Projects...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELauren%20Tickner%2C%20CEO%20of%20a%20British%20marketing%20company%2C%20has%20sparked%20debate%20after%20revealing%20she%20denied%20an%20employee's%20request%20for%20a%20two-day%20leave%20to%20attend%20their%20own%20wedding.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20twist.%20Ms%20Tickner%20took%20to%20Threads%20to%20justify%20her%20decision%2C%20claiming%20the%20employee%20had%20already%20taken%202.5%20weeks%20off%20and%20failed%20to%20train%20a%20replacement%2C%20jeopardising%20two%20critical%20projects.%20Initially%2C%20the%20CEO%20stated%20that%20the%20employee's%20lack%20of%20preparation%20and%20training%20for%20a%20replacement%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20denying%20leave.%20She%20emphasied%20the%20team's%20pressing%20deadlines%20and%20instructed%20the%20employee%20to%20find%20and%20train%20a%20substitute%20before%20taking%20time%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20she%20clarified%20her%20earlier%20statement%20and%20highlighted%20the%20company's%20'flexible%20time%20off'%20policy%20that%20allows%20employees%20to%20take%20leave%20without%C2%A0managerial%20approval.%20Despite%20denying%20the%20initial%20request%2C%20Ms%20Tickner%20told%20the%20employee%20to%20use%20the%20unlimited%20time%20off%20policy%20for%20future%20absences%2C%20bypassing%20the%20need%20for%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20called%20Flexible%20Time%20Off.%20(The%20opposite%20of%20micromanagement%20%26amp%3B%20outdated%20policies).-%20Your%20employees%20set%20their%20hours.%20-%20They%20work%20where%20they%20want.%20-%20They%20take%20days%20off%20when%20they%20choose%2C''%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20biggest%20benefit%3F%20A-players%20don't%20respect%20slackers.%20Anyone%20taking%20too%20much%20time%20off%20loses%20status.%20Flexible%20Time%20Off%20is%20a%20policy%20that%20creates%20trusting%20teams.%20What's%20your%20approach%20to%20unlimited%20time%20off%3F''%2C%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-text-post-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40laurentickner%2Fpost%2FDBTlA_YSYQ5%5C%22%20data-text-post-version%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40laurentickner%2Fpost%2FDBTlA_YSYQ5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40laurentickner%2Fpost%2FDBTlA_YSYQ5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPost%20by%20%40laurentickner%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40laurentickner%2Fpost%2FDBTlA_YSYQ5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20on%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20has%20ignited%20debate%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20many%20users%20being%20confused%20by%20her%20approach.%20Some%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20hypocrisy%2C%20highlighting%20that%20Ms%20Tickner's%20actions%20contradicted%20her%20company's%20Flexible%20Time%20Off%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Firstly%2C%20finding%20and%20training%20a%20replacement%20is%20the%20manager's%20job%2C%20not%20the%20employee's.%20Secondly%2C%20what%20if%20there%20is%20no%20replacement%20available%3F%20Do%20they%20still%20get%20to%20take%20time%20off%3F%20No%3F%20it's%20not%20unlimited%20time%20off%20then%2C%20is%20it%3F''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''The%20part%20I%20don't%20like%20is%20anyone%20taking%20too%20much%20time%20off%20loses%20status.%20You%20are%20pretty%20much-guiding%20people%20into%20not%20using%20their%20PTO.%20And%20who%20determines%20what%20too%20much%20time%20is%3F%20Some%20employers%20might%20think%202%20weeks%20a%20year%20is%20the%20most%20a%20person%20needs.%20I%20would%20disagree.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20her%20attempts%20to%20address%20the%20backlash%20only%20fueled%20further%20confusion%2C%20despite%20her%20repeated%20requests%20for%20people%20to%20%26quot%3Bread%20till%20the%20end%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20explanations.%20She%20also%20faced%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Brage-baiting%26quot%3B%20after%20many%20suggested%20she%20deliberately%20crafted%20a%20provocative%20post%20to%20stir%20controversy%20and%20boost%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20person%20stated%2C%20''So%20you%20offer%20unlimited%20time%20off%20but%20refuse%20time%20off%20for%20the%20biggest%20day%20of%20their%20lives%3F%20And%20why%20is%20it%20your%20employee's%20job%20to%20train%20someone%20to%20replace%20them%20it's%20yours%20surely.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Train%20a%20replacement%20for%202%20days%3F%20To%20get%20married%3F%20If%20your%20team%20can't%20function%20without%20one%20person%20for%20TWO%20DAYS%2C%20and%20you%20can't%20help%20with%20their%20tasks%20or%20delegate%20them%2C%20then%20you%20aren't%20running%20your%20team%20very%20well.%20I%20hope%20this%20post%20was%20rage%20bait%20because%20it's%20gross%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20fourth%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729495080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F695bmj5_lauren-tickner_625x300_21_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fceo-denies-employees-2-day-wedding-leave-we-have-2-critical-projects-6837430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Initially%2C%20the%20CEO%20stated%20that%20the%20employee's%20lack%20of%20preparation%20and%20training%20for%20a%20replacement%20was%20the%20reason%20for%20denying%20leave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fceo-denies-employees-2-day-wedding-leave-we-have-2-critical-projects-6837430%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oberoi%20Realty%20sells%20flats%20worth%20Rs%201.3K%20cr%20in%203%20days%20of%20Maha%20project%20launch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494937000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Foberoi-realty-sells-flats-worth-rs-1-3k-cr-in-3-days-of-maha-project-launch-124102100289_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20October%2018%2C%20the%20company%20launched%20project%20'Oberoi%20Garden%20City%20Thane'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Foberoi-realty-sells-flats-worth-rs-1-3k-cr-in-3-days-of-maha-project-launch-124102100289_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OnePlus%2013%20unveiled%2C%20launch%20in%20China%20set%20for%20Oct%2031%3A%20Check%20design%2C%20features%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Foneplus-13-unveiled-launch-in-china-set-for-oct-31-check-design-features-124102100380_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20OnePlus%2013%20features%20a%20flat%20frame%20design%20and%20a%20flat%20display.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20departure%20from%20common%20rounded%20corners%2C%20the%20smartphone%20sports%20angled%20corners%20on%20all%20sides%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Foneplus-13-unveiled-launch-in-china-set-for-oct-31-check-design-features-124102100380_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Don't%20Want%20India%20To%20Be%20Secular%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20Preamble%20Petitions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20terms%20%26quot%3Bsocialist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsecular%26quot%3B%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Constitution's%20basic%20structure%20and%20the%20courts%20have%20repeatedly%20emphasised%20this%20in%20multiple%20judgments%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%20The%20court%20made%20the%20remarks%20while%20hearing%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20seeking%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20terms%20from%20the%20Preamble%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20is%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20MP%20Subramanian%20Swamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20before%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20PV%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20petitioner%20and%20advocate%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%20said%20the%2042nd%20Amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20in%201976%2C%20which%20affected%20these%20changes%2C%20was%20never%20debated%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20responded%20that%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20debated%20at%20length.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20see%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20the%20words%20have%20varied%20interpretation.%20Both%20words%20have%20different%20interpretations%20today.%20Even%20our%20courts%20have%20declared%20them%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20(of%20the%20Constitution)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSocialism%20can%20also%20mean%20there%20has%20to%20be%20fair%20opportunity%20for%20all%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20equality.%20Let's%20not%20take%20it%20in%20the%20Western%20concept.%20It%20can%20have%20some%20different%20meaning%20as%20well.%20Same%20with%20the%20word%20secularism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Ashwini%20Upadhyay%2C%20also%20a%20petitioner%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20during%20which%20this%20amendment%20was%20affected.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20much%20on%20what%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna%20did%20and%20saved%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Upadhyay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%201976%20judgment%20that%20held%20that%20a%20person's%20right%20to%20not%20be%20unlawfully%20detained%20could%20be%20suspended%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20State.%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna%20was%20the%20lone%20dissenting%20voice%20in%20the%204-1%20judgment%20of%20the%20Constitution%20bench.%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20is%20Justice%20HR%20Khanna's%20nephew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20lawyers'%20arguments%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20India%20to%20be%20secular%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Jain%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20saying%20India%20is%20not%20secular.%20We%20are%20challenging%20this%20amendment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20right%20to%20equality%20and%20the%20word%20'fraternity'%20used%20in%20(the)%20Constitution%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rights%20under%20Part%20III%2C%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20indication%20that%20secular%20has%20been%20held%20as%20the%20core%20feature%20of%20(the)%20Constitution.%20I%20can%20cite%20cases%20for%20you.%20When%20secularism%20was%20debated%2C%20there%20was%20only%20the%20French%20model.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20struck%20down%20statutes%20that%20go%20against%20secularism.%20You%20may%20look%20at%20Article%2025.%20For%20socialism%2C%20we%20have%20not%20followed%20the%20Western%20concept%20and%20we%20are%20happy%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar%20opined%20that%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20word%20'socialism'%20would%20curtail%20liberty%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BHas%20liberty%20been%20curtailed%3F%20Tell%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Upadhyay%20said%20the%20addition%20of%20these%20two%20words%20to%20the%20Preamble%20opened%20a%20Pandora's%20box.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20been%20secular.%20By%20this%20insertion%2C%20a%20box%20has%20been%20opened%2C%20tomorrow%20the%20word%20democracy%20can%20be%20removed%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20argued.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20will%20of%20the%20people%20during%20the%20insertion%20of%20these%20words.%20No%20will%20of%20'we%20the%20people'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20would%20have%20been%20numerous%20legislations%20which%20may%20have%20been%20passed%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20said%20the%20Preamble%20mentions%20the%20date%20November%2026%2C%201949.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20present%20how%20this%20is%20wrong.%20This%20could%20be%20somewhere%20else%20but%20not%20in%20the%20Preamble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20have%20a%20Preamble%20in%20two%20parts.%20It%20is%20wrong%20to%20say%20that%20we%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20consented%20towards%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20words%20'secularism'%20and%20'socialist'.%20There%20could%20be%20two%20parts%20of%20the%20Preamble%2C%20one%20with%20the%20date%20and%20one%20without%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20asked%20the%20petitioners%20to%20submit%20relevant%20documents%20so%20it%20could%20examine%20them.%20The%20bench%20refused%20to%20issue%20notices%20and%20said%20the%20matter%20would%20be%20listed%20next%20on%20November%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Fvoni7s98_supreme-court-new_650x400_12_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-preamble-constitution-you-dont-want-india-to-be-secular-supreme-court-on-preamble-petitions-6837455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20terms%20%26quot%3Bsocialist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsecular%26quot%3B%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Constitution's%20basic%20structure%20and%20the%20courts%20have%20repeatedly%20emphasised%20this%20in%20multiple%20judgments%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-preamble-constitution-you-dont-want-india-to-be-secular-supreme-court-on-preamble-petitions-6837455%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSome%20Jobs%20Reduced%20Due%20To%20AI%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Sunil%20Mittal%20At%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fndtv-world-summit-2024-167%2F%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtvworld_world%2520site%5C%22%3ENDTV%20World%20Summit%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sunil%20Bharti%20Mittal%2C%20Founder%20and%20Chairperson%20of%20Bharti%20Enterprises%2C%20explained%20how%20the%20rapid%20advancements%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20will%20impact%20everything%20from%20global%20economies%20to%20geopolitics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20drivers%20of%20economy%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20geopolitics.%20But%20there%20will%20be%20misuse%20as%20well%2C%20and%20we%20will%20need%20to%20be%20more%20vigilant%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mittal%20said.%20%26quot%3BNation%20states%20will%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20guardrails.%20One%20will%20have%20to%20be%20vigilant%2C%20society%20will%20have%20to%20be%20protected%20from%20the%20evils%20of%20AI.%20I%20remain%20very%20optimistic%20of%20the%20various%20use%20of%20AI.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mittal%20said%20that%20while%20some%20jobs%20are%20being%20reduced%20due%20to%20AI%2C%20new%20opportunities%20are%20emerging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRoutine%2C%20mundane%2C%20repetitive%20jobs%20will%20be%20under%20huge%20threat.%20Remain%20hopeful%20that%20new%20ideas%20will%20come%20through%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20new%20jobs.%20We%20will%20be%20serving%20the%20world%20right%20from%20India.%20AI%20allows%20us%20to%20do%20that%20and%20our%20frugal%20innovations%20are%20going%20to%20serve%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mittal%20said%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20state%20of%20India's%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20Mr%20Mittal%20said%20that%20the%20country's%20mobile%20networks%20are%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20superior%26quot%3B%20to%20those%20in%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Europe%2C%20although%20still%20lagging%20behind%20Japan%20and%20Singapore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mittal%20was%20conferred%20an%20Honorary%20Knighthood%20(KBE)%20by%20King%20Charles%20III%20this%20year%2C%20adding%20to%20his%20list%20of%20accolades%2C%20including%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%20in%202007%20and%20his%20leadership%20roles%20at%20the%20B20%20India%20Action%20Council%20and%20the%20International%20Telecommunication%20Union.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-06%2Fssogqg7g_sunil-mittal_625x300_30_June_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-world-summit-some-jobs-reduced-due-to-ai-but-sunil-bharti-mittal-at-ndtv-world-summit-6837440%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Addressing%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%202024%2