e%20of%20USD%202.34%20million%20(Rs%2019.6%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20first%20runners-up%20South%20Africa%20were%20also%20awarded%20a%20cash-prize%20of%20USD%201.17%20million%20(Rs%209.8%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20prize%20for%20India%20as%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20edition%2C%20ICC%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20prize%20money%20will%20not%20only%20be%20limited%20to%20the%20winner%20and%20the%20runners-up%20but%20also%20to%20the%20semi-finalists%20and%20the%20three%20best%20teams%20in%20the%20group%20stage.%20As%20per%20that%20rule%2C%20semi-finalists%20Australia%20and%20West%20Indies%20got%20USD%20675%2C000%20(Rs%205.7%20crore)%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20group%20stage%20rankings%20are%20still%20not%20confirmed%20but%20with%20two%20wins%20in%20four%20matches%2C%20Team%20India%20is%20highly%20likely%20to%20finish%20at%20No%206%20and%20fetch%20the%20prize%20money%20of%20Rs%20USD%20270%2C000%20(Rs%202.25%20crore).%20The%20same%20prize%20money%20will%20be%20given%20to%20all%20the%20three%20best%20teams%20of%20the%20group%20stage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20historic%20Sunday%20for%20New%20Zealand%20cricket%20as%20the%20White%20Ferns%20got%20their%20hands%20on%20the%20ICC%20trophy%20hours%20after%20the%20men%20recorded%20their%20first%20Test%20win%20in%20India%20after%2036%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fa2n2n0io_new-zealand-women-afp_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwomen-s-t20-world-cup%2Fwomens-t20-world-cup-prize-money-winners-new-zealand-receive-rs-19-6-crore-india-get-6837325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20Zealand%20created%20history%20on%20Sunday%20as%20they%20clinched%20the%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20title.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http