63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy80638zgndo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy80638zgndo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcy80638zgndo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David%20Cameron%20Speaks%20About%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Recalls%20A%20Prediction%20He%20Had%20Made%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Britain%20Lord%20David%20Cameron%20today%20spoke%20about%20'The%20India%20Century'%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20During%20his%20interaction%2C%20he%20mentioned%20about%20his%20prediction%20of%20Britain%20having%20an%20India-origin%20prime%20minister%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20prime%20minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20why%20he%20firmly%20believes%20the%2021st%20Century%20is%20indeed%20a%20defining%20one%20as%20India%20emerges%20as%20a%20leading%20global%20power.%20Backing%20India's%20bid%20for%20a%20permanent%20seat%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20Lord%20Cameron%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20India's%20rightful%20place%20to%20be%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%20but%20as%20these%20reforms%20and%20discussions%20take%20time%2C%20it%20is%20reassuring%20to%20see%20India%20being%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Quad%20and%20G20%20groupings%20and%20also%20now%20regularly%20being%20invited%20the%20G7%20Summit%20too%2C%20as%20a%20fellow%20democracy.%20These%20are%20important%20for%20the%20entire%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemembering%20his%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20diaspora%20event%20held%20at%20the%20Wembley%20Stadium%2C%20Lord%20Cameron%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20moments%20that%20hard%20to%20forget.%20As%20a%20party%20leader%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20one%20is%20used%20to%20addressing%20the%20largest%20of%20gatherings%20of%20two%20to%20three%20thousand%20people.%20But%20to%20go%20to%20Wembley%20Stadium%20which%20is%20packed%20with%20more%20than%2085%2C000%20people%20cheering%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20as%20I%20introduced%20him%20was%20quite%20remarkable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20another%20thing%20I%20vividly%20remember%2C%20and%20one%20that%20I%20found%20out%20later%2C%20is%20that%20when%20I%20making%20my%20speech%20at%20Wembley%20introducing%20PM%20Modi%2C%20I%20had%20made%20a%20prediction%20that%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20will%20give%20the%20UK%20its%20first%20women%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20first%20Jewish%20prime%20minister%2C%20and%20also%20the%20first%20Indian-origin%20prime%20minister.%20Little%20did%20I%20know%20that%20that%20prediction%20would%20come%20true%20so%20soon.%20That%20evening%20there%20was%20a%20young%20leader%20sitting%20way%20at%20the%20back%20-%20his%20name%20is%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20UK's%20first%20Indian-origin%20PM%20soon%20after%20that%20prediction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20about%20the%20India-UK%20partnership%2C%20Lord%20Cameron%20said%20he%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20advocate%20of%20it%20since%20the%20early%202000s.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20said%20back%20in%202005%20that%20the%20India-UK%20partnership%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20a%20special%20status%2C%20and%20ties%20must%20be%20a%20privileged%20partnership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20leadership%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Lord%20Cameron%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20admired%20him.%20I%20thought%20he%20was%20a%20very%20good%20prime%20minister.%20He%20was%20extremely%20hard%20working%2C%20highly%20intelligent%2C%20very%20capable%2C%20brilliant%20chairman%20(of%20the%20Conservative%20Party)%20and%20could%20bring%20everyone%20together.%20When%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20become%20his%20foreign%20secretary%2C%20I%20almost%20immediately%20said%20yes%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20difficult%20time%20globally%20with%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20Being%20a%20former%20PM%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20play%20a%20part%20in%20that%20and%20It%20was%20generous%20of%20him%20to%20ask%20me%20to%20be%20his%20foreign%20secretary.%20He%20wanted%20experienced%20people%20to%20be%20with%20him.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20inheritance%20for%20him%20and%20the%20year%20of%20three%20prime%20ministers%20was%20virtually%20impossible%20for%20anyone%20to%20recover%20from.%20But%20Rishi%20brought%20stability%20to%20Britain.%20He%20brought%20inflation%20down%20from%2011%20per%20cent%20to%202%20per%20cent%2C%20he%20strengthened%20our%20relations%20with%20Europe%20and%20even%20with%20India.%20He%20did%20a%20very%20good%20job%20and%20he%20should%20be%20proud%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Lord%20Cameron%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F37kctquo_david-cameron-ndtv-world-summit_625x300_21_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdavid-cameron-speaks-about-rishi-sunak-recalls-a-prediction-he-had-made-6837297%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Britain%20Lord%20David%20Cameron%20today%20spoke%20about%20'The%20India%20Century'%20at%20the%20NDTV%20World%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20During%20his%20interaction%2C%20he%20mentioned%20about%20his%20prediction%20of%20Britain%20having%20an%20India-origin%20prime%20minister%20come%20true.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdavid-cameron-speaks-about-rishi-sunak-recalls-a-prediction-he-had-made-6837297%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanjay-Maanayata%20celebrate%20their%20twins'%20birthday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729494176000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114418516%2Cimgsize-66426.cms%22%2C%22or