gime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexei%20Navalny%20began%20writing%20his%20memoir%2C%20Patriot%2C%20while%20recuperating%20in%20the%20German%20countryside%20after%20being%20poisoned%20with%20Novichok.%20Upon%20his%20return%20to%20Russia%20and%20subsequent%20imprisonment%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20document%20his%20thoughts%20and%20experiences%20through%20notebook%20entries%2C%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20prison%20diaries%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20being%20published%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20reported%20that%20some%20of%20his%20writings%20were%20confiscated%20by%20prison%20officials.%20Patriot%20is%20both%20illuminating%20and%20harrowing%20%E2%80%94%20knowing%20the%20tragic%20outcome%20of%20Alexei%20Navalny's%20story%20makes%20his%20accounts%20of%20mistreatment%20and%20his%20resistance%20resonate%20with%20even%20greater%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYulia%20recounts%20her%20final%20conversations%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20where%20they%20both%20acknowledged%20the%20likelihood%20that%20he%20would%20never%20leave%20prison%20alive.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20let%20my%20brain%20think%20that%20he%20might%20be%20killed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20But%20Alexei's%20humour%20and%20laughter%20remained%20intact%20until%20the%20end%2C%20a%20trait%20Yulia%20calls%20his%20%E2%80%9Csuperpower.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20really%2C%20truly%20laughed%20at%20this%20regime%20and%20at%20Vladimir%20Putin.%20That's%20why%20Vladimir%20Putin%20hated%20him%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729491840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F3a6i2p98_yulia-navalnaya-alexei-navalny-instagram_625x300_21_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Falexei-navalnys-wife-says-want-vladimir-putin-in-same-conditions-like-my-husband-was-6836852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yulia%20Navalnaya%2C%20the%20widow%20of%20Russian%20opposition%20leader%20Alexei%20Navalny%2C%20