m%2C%20and%20it%20introduced%20him%20to%20the%20world%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-millennial-moved-america-philippines-slow-life-debt-free-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20who%20retired%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20idea%20that%20people%20were%20doing%20that.%20I%20just%20thought%20people%20vacationed%2C%20then%20came%20back%20to%20their%209-to-5s%20and%20kept%20on%20with%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%2C%2056%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20really%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20living%20overseas%2C%20especially%20at%20that%20time%20when%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670caf6a3f2165d716e08843%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFred%20Jones%20and%20his%20wife%20left%20Florida%20and%20moved%20to%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand%2C%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20plan%20was%20to%20move%20to%20Ecuador%20after%20he%20retired%2C%20but%20with%20the%20escalating%20violence%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Jones%20and%20his%20wife%20decided%20to%20look%20elsewhere.%20That's%20when%20he%20remembered%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20Vietnam%20back%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20only%20nine%20days%2C%20but%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2019%2C%202023%2C%20Jones%20retired%20from%20law%20enforcement%20after%2026%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20month%20later%2C%20he%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20his%20wife%20packed%20up%20their%20lives%2C%20sold%20their%20house%2C%20and%20left%20Lake%20County%2C%20Florida%2C%20to%20embark%20on%20their%20next%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourist-mistakes-thailand-chiang-mai-guide-list-holiday-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChiang%20Mai%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20province%20in%20northern%20Thailand%2C%20sight%20unseen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c673279f-70e7-42fd-987f-753ef6f8192e%5C%22%3EMoving%20halfway%20around%20the%20globe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChiang%20Mai%20is%20about%20450%20miles%20north%20of%20Bangkok.%20It%20has%20long%20been%20a%20popular%20destination%20for%20tourists%20and%20expats%20alike%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20stunning%20ancient%20temples%2C%20bustling%20markets%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-cities-for-digital-nomad-remote-work-move-live-abroad-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelatively%20low%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20says%20he%20decided%20to%20move%20there%20after%20doing%20his%20research%20and%20speaking%20to%20people%20he%20met%20on%20expat%20Facebook%20groups%20who%20had%20been%20living%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670e2f9c6ac7b701e7cafd06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20a%20house%20with%20a%20large%20yard%20for%20their%20dog.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20hard%20enough%2C%20there's%20a%20road%20map%20out%20there%20for%20you%20to%20follow%20and%20adjust%20accordingly%20to%20what%20you%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20being%20a%20cop%20has%20prepared%20him%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20unknown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20he%20chose%20Chiang%20Mai%20was%20because%20he%20enjoyed%20northern%20Thai%20cuisine%20and%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20a%20place%20that%20was%20quiet%20but%20still%20easily%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20go%20somewhere%20where%20I%20didn't%20have%20all%20the%20noise%20of%20a%20city%2C%20but%20I%20had%20the%20conveniences%20right%20up%20the%20road%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20decided%20to%20rent%20instead%20of%20buying%20a%20house.%20To%20him%2C%20it%20didn't%20make%20sense%20to%20purchase%20property%20in%20a%20new%20country%20without%20familiarizing%20himself%20with%20the%20different%20areas%20where%20he%20could%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sofa%20in%20the%20office.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670cb4f63f2165d716e0886d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInstead%20of%20buying%20a%20place%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20rent%20instead.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%20with%20you%2C%20we'll%20probably%20rent%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20lives%20unless%20we%20find%20a%20special%20place%20that%20we%20want%20to%20call%20our%20home%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Jones%20and%20his%20wife%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-jet-vacation-japan-toy-poodle-dog-expensive-holiday-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflew%20their%20dog%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Thailand%2C%20they%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20modern%20house%20with%20a%20yard.%20They%20put%20an%20ad%20on%20Facebook%20and%20ended%20up%20finding%20a%20place%20to%20live%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two-bedroom%20house%20is%20slightly%20under%201%2C200%20square%20feet%20and%20is%20located%20in%20Doi%20Saket%2C%20about%2020%20minutes%20east%20of%20Chiang%20Mai%20city%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Chiang%20Mai%20province.%20It%20had%20everything%20they%20needed%2C%20including%20air%20conditioning%20and%20even%20an%20oven.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20house%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20isn't%20that%20different%20from%20their%20house%20back%20in%20Florida.%20Both%20had%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20except%20the%20couple%20had%20a%20bigger%20kitchen%20and%20a%20garage%20back%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20comfortable.%20It%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20well-built%2C%20and%20he%20said%20it%20would%20take%20care%20of%20any%20kind%20of%20maintenance%20that%20was%20required.%20He%20even%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20lawn%2C%20so%20that's%20a%20bonus%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20their%C2%A0landlord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670cb4f56ac7b701e7cac26d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETheir%20house%20came%20with%20everything%20they%20needed%2C%20including%20a%20kitchen%20oven.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERent%20is%2018%2C000%20Thai%20baht%2C%20or%20about%20%24540%2C%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20sits%20on%20an%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20and%20while%20the%20couple%20has%20neighbors%20about%2025%20yards%20to%20their%20left%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Bnever%20hear%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20local%20market%20is%20a%20five-minute%20walk%20away%2C%20with%20bigger%20grocery%20stores%20nearby%20that%20stock%20Western%20brands%20as%20well.%20Coffee%20shops%20are%20aplenty%20in%20their%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20there's%20even%20an%20Italian%20restaurant%20for%20when%20their%20pasta%20craving%20hits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f01d24d8-9e3b-4284-a75d-d4b3466433c6%5C%22%3EFinding%20their%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Jones%20and%20his%20wife%20not%20knowing%20anyone%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20Chiang%20Mai%20before%20their%20move%2C%20they%20found%20a%20community%20qu