ance%20for%20him%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20as%20well%20as%20miscellaneous%20travel%20expenses%20like%20a%20vacation%20to%20a%20nearby%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20probably%20living%20on%20a%20third%20of%20what%20we%20would%20be%20spending%20in%20the%20United%20States%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670f343b3f2165d716e19895%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJones%20says%20he%20feels%20safer%20in%20Chiang%20Mai.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c53bd60-736f-49e0-b088-9eeef1611138%5C%22%3EFeeling%20safer%20has%20lowered%20stress%20levels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECost%20of%20living%20aside%2C%20Jones%20says%20his%20mental%20health%20has%20greatly%20improved%20since%20he%20started%20living%20in%20Chiang%20Mai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20realized%20how%20hypervigilant%20I%20was%20all%20the%20time%2C%20even%20off-duty%2C%20until%20I%20moved%20here.%20It's%20just%20like%20all%20the%20stress%2C%20having%20your%20head%20on%20the%20swivel%2C%20all%20of%20that%20stuff%20just%20disappeared%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20law%20enforcement%20back%20in%20Florida%20meant%20that%20he%20had%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20trauma%20while%20on%20the%20job.%20Some%20of%20these%20incidents%20stayed%20with%20him%20long%20after%20he%20clocked%20out%20of%20his%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20weekends%2C%20if%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20going%20to%20a%20movie%20or%20somewhere%2C%20we%20would%20pass%20by%20places%20that%20I%20could%20look%20at%20and%20say%2C%20'That%20homicide%20happened%20over%20there'%20or%20'That%20rape%20happened%20over%20there%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20relive%20those%20things%20in%20your%20head%20over%20and%20over%20again%20when%20you%20live%20in%20the%20same%20place%20where%20you've%20seen%20all%20this%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20has%20given%20him%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20beginning%20where%20none%20of%20that%20occupies%20my%20mind%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osac.gov%2FCountry%2FThailand%2FContent%2FDetail%2FReport%2F33ef53fa-45cf-409c-8398-1c49361d4481%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20crime%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siam-legal.com%2Fthailand-law%2Fare-guns-legal-in-thailand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrict%20gun%20control%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jones%20also%20feels%20safer%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20than%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20fact%2C%20ever%20since%20he%20arrived%20in%20Asia%2C%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20sit%20with%20his%20back%20to%20the%20door%20%E2%80%94%20something%20he%20never%20used%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20I%20mean%20by%20it%20being%20life-changing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218c3800e-a3c2-4b15-abd5-8c038340c512%5C%22%3ELiving%20life%20on%20his%20own%20terms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20best%20part%20about%20being%20retired%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20is%20that%20he%20has%20the%20freedom%20to%20do%20whatever%20he%20wants%20with%20his%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20his%20dog%20in%20the%20car.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670f3472a70318649282ac10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJones%20says%20he%20now%20has%20time%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20his%20loved%20ones%2C%20including%20his%20dog.%3Cp%3EFred%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20he's%20no%20longer%20bogged%20down%20by%20work%2C%20he%20gets%20to%20indulge%20in%20his%20hobbies%20and%2