2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20manage%20these%20dogs%2C%20they%20are%20housed%20in%20different%20pens.%20For%20instance%2C%20older%20dogs%20and%20dogs%20receiving%20medication%20and%20treatments%20are%20grouped%20in%20the%20largest%20pen%20measuring%20100%20x%20100%20feet.%20Dogs%20which%20are%20younger%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20more%20active%2C%20are%20housed%20in%20a%20separate%20pen.%C2%A0Young%20pups%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20grouped%20in%20another%20pen.%20One%20pen%20is%20specifically%20dedicated%20to%20a%20Tibetan%20Mastiff.%20On%20the%20outside%2C%20he%20developed%20a%20reputation%20for%20being%20aggressive%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20owner%20had%20to%20surrender%20him%20because%20he%20had%20bitten%20several%20people.%20We%20gave%20him%20his%20own%20pen%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20female%20dogs%2C%20and%20he%20gets%20along%20fine%20with%20them%20and%20the%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESemchan%E2%80%99s%20unique%20approach%20to%20stray%20dog%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20rescue%20service%20has%20become%20pretty%20well-known%20in%20Leh.%20Our%20phone%20number%20is%20available%20in%20the%20community%2C%20so%20people%20call%20the%20team.%20The%20caller%20is%20asked%20to%20send%20a%20picture%20or%20video%20of%20the%20dog%20needing%20rescue%20and%20to%20stay%20there%20with%20the%20dog%20while%20we%20come.%20Usually%2C%20two%20men%20take%20the%20van%2C%20which%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20cage%20for%20capturing%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nurzin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20uses%20careful%20and%20compassionate%20capture%20methods%2C%20almost%20always%20without%20nets%20or%20ropes.%20They%20usually%20cover%20the%20dog%20with%20a%20blanket%2C%20scoop%20it%20up%20into%20their%20arms%2C%20and%20quickly%20put%20it%20into%20the%20cage.%20Then%20we%20take%20the%20dog%20to%20the%20government%20veterinary%20hospital%20for%20examination%20and%2For%20treatment.%20Once