.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20expect%20your%20family%20to%20understand%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20going%20through%20right%20away.%20It%20takes%20time.%20The%20major%20thing%20people%20need%20to%20realise%20is%20that%20people%20with%20anxiety%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20advice%20or%20solutions.%20We%20just%20want%20to%20be%20heard.%20We%20can%20find%20our%20own%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20what%20helped%20Rama%20cope%20with%20her%20anxiety%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETry%20journalling%3A%20%E2%80%98It%20helped%20me%20expand%20my%20thoughts.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETake%20support%20from%20friends%20and%20family%3A%20She%20worked%20out%20of%20a%20friend%E2%80%99s%20house%20as%20she%20was%20afraid%20of%20being%20alone.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESlow%20down%3A%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99ve%20learnt%20not%20to%20get%20bogged%20down%20by%20new%20experiences.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESpend%20time%20in%20the%20sun%3A%20%E2%80%98It%20can%20positively%20impact%20your%20hormones%2C%20making%20you%20hopeful.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGo%20on%20long%20walks%3A%20It%20can%20help%20you%20clear%20your%20mind.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBe%20vulnerable%3A%20Speaking%20about%20her%20anxiety%20with%20colleagues%20has%20helped.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20her%20worldview%20has%20changed%2C%20as%20she%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20hustle%20culture%20anymore.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20part%20of%20anything%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20me%20to%20rest%20or%20impacts%20my%20mental%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20if%20she%20had%20a%2