figure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shares%20a%20horrifying%20discovery%20proving%20that%20criminal%20abortions%20are%20true%20to%20their%20name%20for%20more%20reasons%20than%20one.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20procedures%20were%20usually%20done%20by%20male%20%E2%80%98quacks%E2%80%99%20who%20would%20extract%20money%20from%20the%20woman%20and%20her%20family.%20Post%20the%20procedure%2C%20they%20would%20indulge%20in%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20the%20woman%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F91667%2Fdurgaiah-throat-cancer-survivor-fight-tobacco-addiction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvocacy%20programmes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20urges%20doctors%20and%20medical%20workers%20to%20take%20cognisance%20of%20these%20outmoded%20sensibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrain%20more%20doctors%20to%20conduct%20caesareans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20the%20very%20first%20case%20that%20you%20dealt%20with%3F%20I%20ask%20Dr%20Rani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20memory%2C%20I%20deduce%2C%20is%20perfect%2C%20as%20she%20recalls%20being%20called%20upon%20by%20the%20district%20hospital%20to%20attend%20to%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20in%20distress.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20labour%20was%20obstructed%20and%20prolonged.%20I%20checked%20for%20foetal%20heart%20sounds%2C%20they%20were%20absent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhealthcare-access-in-tribal-areas-5-1728468177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gadchiroli%20now%20has%20trained%20nurses%20and%20healthcare%20practitioners%20who%20can%20perform%20C-sections%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20lower%20maternal%20mortalities%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2