and%20the%20impact%20and%20the%20damage%20they%20inflict%20on%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Do%20not%20treat%20domestic%20abuse%20survivors%20as%20cheap%20labour%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20times%2C%20people%20reach%20out%20to%20Prasanna%20offering%20jobs%20such%20as%20taking%20care%20of%20senior%20citizens%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20working%20as%20domestic%20helpers%2C%20or%20stitching%20bags%20for%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20not%20all%20survivors%20of%20violence%20can%20stitch%20bags%20for%20a%20living.%20If%20a%20survivor%20decides%20to%20leave%20the%20perpetrator%20and%20become%20financially%20independent%20to%20take%20care%20of%20herself%20and%20their%20children%2C%20we%20cannot%20tell%20them%20that%20you%20can%20be%20a%20source%20of%20cheap%20labour%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20believes%20that%20every%20individual%20has%20their%20own%20strengths%2C%20and%20opportunities%20should%20be%20offered%20to%20them%20based%20on%20those%20strengths.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-1-1728394794-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20cl